<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>SB-Relais — Simulation de Devis</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=Jost:wght@200;300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --or: #b8883a;
    --or-clair: #e8c97a;
    --creme: #f9f6f0;
    --creme-fonce: #ede8e0;
    --brun: #2a2016;
    --brun-mid: #5a4a2e;
    --brun-light: #8a7a5a;
    --blanc: #ffffff;
    --rouge: #c0392b;
    --vert: #27ae60;
  }

- { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

body {
background: var(–creme-fonce);
font-family: ‘Jost’, sans-serif;
min-height: 100vh;
}

/* ── HEADER ── */
.site-header {
background: var(–creme);
border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(184,136,58,0.2);
padding: 20px 40px;
display: flex;
align-items: center;
justify-content: center;
position: relative;
}

.site-header::after {
content: ‘’;
position: absolute;
bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
height: 2px;
background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 5%, var(–or) 30%, var(–or-clair) 50%, var(–or) 70%, transparent 95%);
}

.header-logo {
display: flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 0;
}

.header-rule {
width: 24px; height: 1px;
background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(–or));
}
.header-rule.right {
background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(–or), transparent);
}

.header-sb {
font-family: ‘Cormorant Garamond’, serif;
font-weight: 400;
font-size: 28px;
letter-spacing: 3px;
color: var(–brun);
padding: 0 8px;
}

.header-sep {
width: 1px; height: 24px;
background: var(–or);
margin: 0 3px;
opacity: 0.7;
}

.header-relais {
font-family: ‘Cormorant Garamond’, serif;
font-weight: 300;
font-size: 28px;
letter-spacing: 5px;
color: var(–brun);
padding: 0 8px;
}

/* ── PAGE LAYOUT ── */
.page {
max-width: 720px;
margin: 0 auto;
padding: 50px 24px 80px;
}

/* ── TITRE PAGE ── */
.page-title {
text-align: center;
margin-bottom: 40px;
}

.page-title h1 {
font-family: ‘Cormorant Garamond’, serif;
font-weight: 300;
font-size: 36px;
color: var(–brun);
letter-spacing: 1px;
margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.page-title p {
font-weight: 300;
font-size: 13px;
letter-spacing: 2px;
color: var(–brun-light);
text-transform: uppercase;
}

.page-title .title-rule {
width: 40px; height: 1px;
background: var(–or);
margin: 14px auto;
}

/* ── CARTE FORMULAIRE ── */
.form-card {
background: var(–creme);
border: 1px solid rgba(184,136,58,0.2);
padding: 40px;
position: relative;
}

.form-card::before {
content: ‘’;
position: absolute;
top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
height: 3px;
background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 5%, var(–or) 30%, var(–or-clair) 50%, var(–or) 70%, transparent 95%);
}

/* ── SECTIONS ── */
.section-title {
font-family: ‘Jost’, sans-serif;
font-weight: 500;
font-size: 10px;
letter-spacing: 4px;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: var(–or);
margin-bottom: 20px;
padding-bottom: 10px;
border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(184,136,58,0.2);
}

.form-section {
margin-bottom: 36px;
}

/* ── CHAMPS ── */
.field {
margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.field label {
display: block;
font-weight: 400;
font-size: 11px;
letter-spacing: 2px;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: var(–brun-mid);
margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.field label .req {
color: var(–or);
margin-left: 3px;
}

.field input,
.field select,
.field textarea {
width: 100%;
background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
border: 1px solid rgba(184,136,58,0.25);
padding: 12px 16px;
font-family: ‘Jost’, sans-serif;
font-weight: 300;
font-size: 14px;
color: var(–brun);
outline: none;
transition: border-color 0.2s;
appearance: none;
}

.field input:focus,
.field select:focus,
.field textarea:focus {
border-color: var(–or);
background: var(–blanc);
}

.field input::placeholder,
.field textarea::placeholder {
color: #c0b090;
font-weight: 200;
}

.field .hint {
margin-top: 6px;
font-size: 11px;
color: var(–brun-light);
font-weight: 300;
font-style: italic;
}

.field .hint.warn {
color: #d4870a;
font-weight: 400;
}

.field-row {
display: grid;
grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
gap: 16px;
}

/* ── VOIE D’EXPÉDITION ── */
.voie-options {
display: flex;
gap: 12px;
}

.voie-option {
flex: 1;
position: relative;
}

.voie-option input[type=“radio”] {
position: absolute;
opacity: 0;
width: 0; height: 0;
}

.voie-option label {
display: flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 10px;
padding: 14px 16px;
border: 1px solid rgba(184,136,58,0.25);
background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
cursor: pointer;
transition: all 0.2s;
font-size: 13px;
letter-spacing: 1px;
text-transform: none;
color: var(–brun-mid);
font-weight: 300;
}

.voie-option input[type=“radio”]:checked + label {
border-color: var(–or);
background: rgba(184,136,58,0.06);
color: var(–brun);
}

.voie-icon {
font-size: 18px;
flex-shrink: 0;
}

/* ── TRANSPORTEUR OUI/NON ── */
.oui-non {
display: flex;
gap: 12px;
margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.oui-non-option {
position: relative;
flex: 1;
}

.oui-non-option input[type=“radio”] {
position: absolute;
opacity: 0;
width: 0; height: 0;
}

.oui-non-option label {
display: block;
text-align: center;
padding: 13px;
border: 1px solid rgba(184,136,58,0.25);
background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
cursor: pointer;
font-family: ‘Cormorant Garamond’, serif;
font-size: 20px;
font-weight: 400;
color: var(–brun-mid);
letter-spacing: 2px;
transition: all 0.2s;
text-transform: none;
}

.oui-non-option input[type=“radio”]:checked + label {
border-color: var(–or);
background: rgba(184,136,58,0.06);
color: var(–brun);
}

/* ── BLOCS CONDITIONNELS ── */
.conditional {
display: none;
margin-top: 16px;
}

.conditional.visible {
display: block;
animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease;
}

@keyframes fadeIn {
from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-6px); }
to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

.info-box {
padding: 14px 18px;
border-left: 3px solid var(–or);
background: rgba(184,136,58,0.05);
font-size: 13px;
color: var(–brun-mid);
font-weight: 300;
line-height: 1.6;
margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.info-box strong {
color: var(–brun);
font-weight: 500;
}

.info-box.partenaire {
border-left-color: #2e7d60;
background: rgba(39,174,96,0.05);
color: #1a5e40;
}

/* ── BOUTON ── */
.btn-submit {
width: 100%;
background: var(–brun);
color: var(–or);
border: none;
padding: 16px;
font-family: ‘Jost’, sans-serif;
font-weight: 300;
font-size: 11px;
letter-spacing: 5px;
text-transform: uppercase;
cursor: pointer;
transition: background 0.2s;
margin-top: 10px;
}

.btn-submit:hover {
background: #1a1008;
}

/* ── RÉSULTAT DEVIS ── */
#resultat {
display: none;
margin-top: 32px;
}

#resultat.visible {
display: block;
animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease;
}

.resultat-card {
background: var(–creme);
border: 1px solid rgba(184,136,58,0.3);
position: relative;
overflow: hidden;
}

.resultat-card::before {
content: ‘’;
position: absolute;
top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
height: 3px;
background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 5%, var(–or) 30%, var(–or-clair) 50%, var(–or) 70%, transparent 95%);
}

.resultat-header {
padding: 28px 36px 20px;
border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(184,136,58,0.15);
}

.resultat-header h2 {
font-family: ‘Cormorant Garamond’, serif;
font-weight: 300;
font-size: 28px;
color: var(–brun);
margin-bottom: 4px;
}

.resultat-header p {
font-size: 12px;
letter-spacing: 2px;
color: var(–brun-light);
text-transform: uppercase;
font-weight: 300;
}

.resultat-body {
padding: 28px 36px;
}

.recap-row {
display: flex;
justify-content: space-between;
align-items: center;
padding: 12px 0;
border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(184,136,58,0.1);
font-size: 14px;
}

.recap-row:last-child {
border-bottom: none;
}

.recap-label {
color: var(–brun-mid);
font-weight: 300;
letter-spacing: 1px;
}

.recap-value {
color: var(–brun);
font-weight: 400;
text-align: right;
}

.recap-value.gold {
color: var(–or);
font-family: ‘Cormorant Garamond’, serif;
font-size: 20px;
font-weight: 600;
}

.recap-value.transport-libre {
color: var(–vert);
font-size: 12px;
letter-spacing: 1px;
}

/* Stockage */
.stockage-badge {
display: inline-block;
background: rgba(184,136,58,0.1);
border: 1px solid rgba(184,136,58,0.3);
color: var(–or);
font-size: 11px;
letter-spacing: 2px;
text-transform: uppercase;
padding: 4px 12px;
font-weight: 400;
}

/* Articles interdits */
.interdits-section {
margin-top: 24px;
padding: 20px;
background: rgba(192,57,43,0.04);
border: 1px solid rgba(192,57,43,0.2);
border-left: 3px solid var(–rouge);
}

.interdits-title {
font-size: 10px;
letter-spacing: 3px;
text-transform: uppercase;
color: var(–rouge);
font-weight: 500;
margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.interdits-list {
list-style: none;
display: grid;
grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
gap: 6px 20px;
}

.interdits-list li {
font-size: 12px;
color: var(–brun-mid);
font-weight: 300;
display: flex;
align-items: center;
gap: 6px;
}

.interdits-list li::before {
content: ‘×’;
color: var(–rouge);
font-weight: 600;
font-size: 14px;
flex-shrink: 0;
}

.interdits-warning {
margin-top: 14px;
font-size: 11px;
color: var(–rouge);
font-weight: 400;
line-height: 1.6;
font-style: italic;
}

.resultat-footer {
padding: 20px 36px 28px;
border-top: 1px solid rgba(184,136,58,0.15);
text-align: center;
}

.resultat-footer p {
font-size: 12px;
color: var(–brun-light);
font-weight: 300;
line-height: 1.7;
}

.resultat-footer strong {
color: var(–or);
font-weight: 500;
}

.btn-reset {
margin-top: 16px;
background: transparent;
border: 1px solid rgba(184,136,58,0.4);
color: var(–brun-mid);
padding: 10px 28px;
font-family: ‘Jost’, sans-serif;
font-weight: 300;
font-size: 10px;
letter-spacing: 3px;
text-transform: uppercase;
cursor: pointer;
transition: all 0.2s;
}

.btn-reset:hover {
border-color: var(–or);
color: var(–or);
}

/* Erreur champ */
.tel-wrapper {
display: flex;
align-items: center;
border: 1px solid rgba(184,136,58,0.25);
background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
transition: border-color 0.2s;
}

.tel-wrapper:focus-within {
border-color: var(–or);
background: var(–blanc);
}

.tel-indicatif {
padding: 0 12px;
font-size: 13px;
font-weight: 400;
color: var(–brun);
background: rgba(184,136,58,0.06);
border-right: 1px solid rgba(184,136,58,0.2);
white-space: nowrap;
height: 100%;
display: flex;
align-items: center;
min-height: 44px;
letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

.tel-wrapper input {
border: none;
background: transparent;
flex: 1;
padding: 12px 14px;
}

.tel-wrapper input:focus {
outline: none;
background: transparent;
}

.field.invalid .tel-wrapper {
border-color: var(–rouge);
}

.field.invalid input,
.field.invalid select {
border-color: var(–rouge);
}

.field-error {
margin-top: 5px;
font-size: 11px;
color: rgba(184,136,58,0.4);
font-style: italic;
font-weight: 300;
letter-spacing: 0.5px;
display: block;
}

.field.invalid .field-error {
display: block;
color: var(–rouge);
font-style: normal;
font-weight: 400;
}

/* ── RGPD ── */
.rgpd-section {
margin-top: 24px;
margin-bottom: 20px;
padding: 18px 20px;
border: 1px solid rgba(184,136,58,0.2);
background: rgba(184,136,58,0.03);
}

.rgpd-label {
display: flex;
gap: 12px;
align-items: flex-start;
cursor: pointer;
font-size: 12px;
color: var(–brun-mid);
font-weight: 300;
line-height: 1.6;
text-transform: none;
letter-spacing: 0;
}

.rgpd-label input[type=“checkbox”] {
width: 16px;
height: 16px;
flex-shrink: 0;
margin-top: 2px;
accent-color: var(–or);
cursor: pointer;
}

.rgpd-label strong {
color: var(–brun);
font-weight: 500;
}

.rgpd-error {
margin-top: 8px;
font-size: 11px;
color: var(–rouge);
display: none;
padding-left: 28px;
}

.rgpd-error.visible {
display: block;
}

/* Notice RGPD dans le résultat */
.rgpd-notice {
margin: 16px 0;
padding: 14px 16px;
background: rgba(184,136,58,0.04);
border-left: 3px solid rgba(184,136,58,0.4);
font-size: 11px;
color: var(–brun-mid);
font-weight: 300;
line-height: 1.7;
text-align: left;
}

.rgpd-notice strong {
color: var(–brun);
font-weight: 500;
}

@media (max-width: 560px) {
.form-card { padding: 24px 20px; }
.interdits-list { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
.voie-options { flex-direction: column; }
.resultat-body { padding: 20px; }
.resultat-header { padding: 20px 20px 14px; }
.resultat-footer { padding: 14px 20px 20px; }
}
</style>

</head>
<body>

<!-- HEADER -->

<header class="site-header">
  <div class="header-logo">
    <div class="header-rule"></div>
    <span class="header-sb">SB</span>
    <div class="header-sep"></div>
    <span class="header-relais">Relais</span>
    <div class="header-rule right"></div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- PAGE -->

<div class="page">

  <div class="page-title">
    <h1>Simulation de Devis</h1>
    <div class="title-rule"></div>
    <p>Pont logistique · Occident &amp; Afrique</p>
  </div>

  <!-- FORMULAIRE -->

  <div class="form-card">

```
<!-- SECTION 1 : IDENTITÉ -->
<div class="form-section">
  <div class="section-title">01 — Vos informations</div>

  <div class="field-row">
    <div class="field" id="f-nom">
      <label>Nom <span class="req">*</span></label>
      <input type="text" id="nom" placeholder="Votre nom de famille">
      <div class="field-error">Ce champ est obligatoire.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="field" id="f-prenom">
      <label>Prénom <span class="req">*</span></label>
      <input type="text" id="prenom" placeholder="Votre prénom">
      <div class="field-error">Ce champ est obligatoire.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="field" id="f-pays">
    <label>Pays d'expédition <span class="req">*</span></label>
    <select id="pays">
      <option value="">— Sélectionnez votre pays —</option>
      <optgroup label="Afrique de l'Ouest">
        <option>Côte d'Ivoire 🇨🇮</option>
        <option>Sénégal 🇸🇳</option>
        <option>Mali 🇲🇱</option>
        <option>Guinée 🇬🇳</option>
        <option>Burkina Faso 🇧🇫</option>
        <option>Togo 🇹🇬</option>
        <option>Bénin 🇧🇯</option>
        <option>Niger 🇳🇪</option>
        <option>Ghana 🇬🇭</option>
        <option>Nigeria 🇳🇬</option>
        <option>Mauritanie 🇲🇷</option>
        <option>Sierra Leone 🇸🇱</option>
        <option>Liberia 🇱🇷</option>
        <option>Guinée-Bissau 🇬🇼</option>
        <option>Gambie 🇬🇲</option>
        <option>Cap-Vert 🇨🇻</option>
      </optgroup>
      <optgroup label="Afrique Centrale">
        <option>Cameroun 🇨🇲</option>
        <option>Congo-Brazzaville 🇨🇬</option>
        <option>RD Congo 🇨🇩</option>
        <option>Gabon 🇬🇦</option>
        <option>Tchad 🇹🇩</option>
        <option>République Centrafricaine 🇨🇫</option>
        <option>Guinée Équatoriale 🇬🇶</option>
        <option>São Tomé-et-Príncipe 🇸🇹</option>
      </optgroup>
      <optgroup label="Afrique de l'Est">
        <option>Éthiopie 🇪🇹</option>
        <option>Kenya 🇰🇪</option>
        <option>Tanzanie 🇹🇿</option>
        <option>Rwanda 🇷🇼</option>
        <option>Ouganda 🇺🇬</option>
        <option>Burundi 🇧🇮</option>
        <option>Somalie 🇸🇴</option>
        <option>Djibouti 🇩🇯</option>
        <option>Érythrée 🇪🇷</option>
        <option>Soudan 🇸🇩</option>
        <option>Soudan du Sud 🇸🇸</option>
        <option>Madagascar 🇲🇬</option>
        <option>Comores 🇰🇲</option>
        <option>Seychelles 🇸🇨</option>
        <option>Maurice 🇲🇺</option>
      </optgroup>
      <optgroup label="Afrique du Nord">
        <option>Maroc 🇲🇦</option>
        <option>Algérie 🇩🇿</option>
        <option>Tunisie 🇹🇳</option>
        <option>Libye 🇱🇾</option>
        <option>Égypte 🇪🇬</option>
      </optgroup>
      <optgroup label="Afrique Australe">
        <option>Afrique du Sud 🇿🇦</option>
        <option>Angola 🇦🇴</option>
        <option>Mozambique 🇲🇿</option>
        <option>Zambie 🇿🇲</option>
        <option>Zimbabwe 🇿🇼</option>
        <option>Malawi 🇲🇼</option>
        <option>Namibie 🇳🇦</option>
        <option>Botswana 🇧🇼</option>
        <option>Lesotho 🇱🇸</option>
        <option>Eswatini 🇸🇿</option>
      </optgroup>
    </select>
    <div class="field-error">Veuillez sélectionner votre pays.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="field" id="f-tel">
    <label>Numéro de téléphone <span class="req">*</span></label>
    <div class="tel-wrapper">
      <span class="tel-indicatif" id="tel-indicatif">🌍</span>
      <input type="tel" id="tel" placeholder="6 00 00 00 00">
    </div>
    <div class="field-error">Ce champ est obligatoire.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="field">
    <label>Adresse e-mail</label>
    <input type="email" id="email" placeholder="votre@email.com">
  </div>
</div>

<!-- SECTION 2 : ENVOI -->
<div class="form-section">
  <div class="section-title">02 — Votre envoi</div>

  <div class="field">
    <label>Voie d'expédition <span class="req">*</span></label>
    <div class="voie-options" style="display:flex;flex-direction:row;gap:12px;">
      <div class="voie-option" style="flex:1;">
        <input type="radio" name="voie" id="voie-maritime" value="maritime">
        <label for="voie-maritime" style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;">
          <span class="voie-icon">🚢</span>
          Voie maritime
        </label>
      </div>
      <div class="voie-option" style="flex:1;">
        <input type="radio" name="voie" id="voie-aerien" value="aerien">
        <label for="voie-aerien" style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;">
          <span class="voie-icon">✈️</span>
          Voie aérienne
        </label>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Poids — visible uniquement si maritime -->
  <div class="conditional" id="bloc-poids">
    <div class="field" id="f-poids">
      <label>Poids estimé du colis (kg) <span class="req">*</span></label>
      <input type="number" id="poids" placeholder="Ex : 2.5" min="0.1" step="0.1">
      <div class="hint">Le tarif aérien est calculé au kilogramme.</div>
      <div class="field-error">Veuillez indiquer le poids estimé.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="field" id="f-article">
    <label>Type d'article à envoyer <span class="req">*</span></label>
    <select id="article">
      <option value="">— Sélectionnez une catégorie —</option>
      <option value="vetements">Vêtements &amp; accessoires de mode</option>
      <option value="cosmetiques">Cosmétiques &amp; produits de beauté</option>
      <option value="electronique">Électronique &amp; high-tech</option>
      <option value="jouets">Jouets &amp; articles enfants</option>
      <option value="livres">Livres</option>
      <option value="documents">Documents</option>
      <option value="medicaments">Médicaments</option>
      <option value="meubles">Meubles &amp; mobilier</option>
      <option value="equipement">Équipement professionnel</option>
      <option value="autre">Autre (à préciser)</option>
    </select>
    <div class="field-error">Veuillez sélectionner le type d'article.</div>
    <div class="hint warn" id="hint-meubles" style="display:none;">
      🛋️ Pour les envois de meubles, un conseiller SB-Relais vous contactera pour établir un devis personnalisé.
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Champ visible uniquement si "Autre" sélectionné -->
  <div class="conditional" id="bloc-autre-article">
    <div class="field" id="f-article-autre">
      <label>Précisez le type d'article <span class="req">*</span></label>
      <input type="text" id="article-autre" placeholder="Décrivez l'article à envoyer">
      <div class="field-error">Veuillez préciser le type d'article.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Valeur + état — masqué pour documents et livres -->
  <div class="conditional" id="bloc-valeur">
    <div class="field-row">
      <div class="field" id="f-valeur">
        <label>Valeur déclarée de l'article (€) <span class="req">*</span></label>
        <input type="number" id="valeur" placeholder="Ex : 150" min="0" step="1">
        <div class="hint">Valeur estimée ou prix d'achat de l'article.</div>
        <div class="field-error">Veuillez indiquer la valeur de l'article.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="field" id="f-etat">
        <label>État de l'article <span class="req">*</span></label>
        <select id="etat">
          <option value="">— Sélectionnez —</option>
          <option value="neuf">Neuf</option>
          <option value="occasion">Occasion / Déjà utilisé</option>
        </select>
        <div class="field-error">Veuillez sélectionner l'état.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<!-- SECTION 3 : TRANSPORTEUR -->
<div class="form-section">
  <div class="section-title">03 — Votre transporteur <span style="color:var(--or)">*</span></div>

  <div class="info-box" style="margin-bottom:16px;">
    <strong>📍 Point de collecte :</strong> Les colis sont à récupérer à <strong>Paris (Île-de-France)</strong>. Merci de vous assurer que votre transporteur dessert bien cette zone.
  </div>

  <div class="field">
    <label>Avez-vous un transporteur ? <span class="req">*</span></label>
    <div class="oui-non">
      <div class="oui-non-option">
        <input type="radio" name="transporteur" id="tr-oui" value="oui">
        <label for="tr-oui">Oui</label>
      </div>
      <div class="oui-non-option">
        <input type="radio" name="transporteur" id="tr-non" value="non">
        <label for="tr-non">Non</label>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Si OUI -->
  <div class="conditional" id="bloc-transporteur-oui">
    <div class="field-row">
      <div class="field" id="f-tr-nom">
        <label>Nom du transporteur <span class="req">*</span></label>
        <input type="text" id="tr-nom" placeholder="Nom ou raison sociale">
        <div class="field-error">Ce champ est obligatoire.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="field" id="f-tr-tel">
        <label>Téléphone du transporteur <span class="req">*</span></label>
        <input type="tel" id="tr-tel" placeholder="01 23 45 67 89">
        <div class="hint">Fixe (01–05 et 09) ou mobile (06/07) — format français</div>
        <div class="field-error">Ce champ est obligatoire.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Si NON -->
  <div class="conditional" id="bloc-transporteur-non">
    <div class="info-box partenaire">
      <strong>ℹ️ Information importante :</strong> Nos transporteurs partenaires (voie aérienne et maritime) desservent exclusivement la <strong>Côte d'Ivoire 🇨🇮</strong>. Si votre destination est différente, vous devrez prévoir votre propre transporteur.
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- RGPD -->
<div class="rgpd-section">
  <label class="rgpd-label" for="rgpd-check">
    <input type="checkbox" id="rgpd-check">
    <span>J'accepte que SB-Relais collecte et traite mes données personnelles (nom, téléphone, e-mail, pays) aux seules fins du traitement de ma demande de devis, conformément au <strong>Règlement Général sur la Protection des Données (RGPD)</strong>. Ces données ne seront ni vendues ni cédées à des tiers et seront conservées le temps nécessaire au traitement de ma demande. Je dispose d'un droit d'accès, de rectification et de suppression en contactant SB-Relais. <span class="req">*</span></span>
  </label>
  <div class="rgpd-error" id="rgpd-error">Vous devez accepter la politique de confidentialité pour continuer.</div>
</div>

<button class="btn-submit" onclick="genererDevis()">Obtenir mon devis &rarr;</button>
